OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUnison suspends planned NHS
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fstrike ballot              
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Scotland's largest health union has    
OL,6, suspended its strike ballot of NHS     
OL,7, staff and is consulting on an improved 
OL,8, pay offer.                             
OL,10,FThe Scottish government made a revised 
OL,11,FNHS pay offer on Friday that would see 
OL,12,Fa hike of #2,205 per worker.           
OL,14,FUnison has announced it will suspend   
OL,15,Fplans to ballot its members on         
OL,16,Findustrial action to consider the deal.
OL,18,FBut other health unions are continuing 
OL,19,Fto recommend members reject the offer  
OL,20,Fand vote for strike action.            
